// initTextarea( _g ) 1) initialize variables, 2) attach textbox and 3) create burglish_font seleciton toolbar
// initTextarea( _g, skipAttachment, '1' ) initialize variables skipping last two sequence
function initTextarea( _g, skipAttachment ) {
	_o[_g.id] = new Object();
	_o[_g.id]["list"] = new Array();
	_o[_g.id]["curPos"] = -1;
	_o[_g.id]["count"] = 0;
	_o[_g.id]["query"]="";_o[_g.id]["prev"]="";
	_o[_g.id]["prevW"]="";
	_o[_g.id]["noitem"]=0;
	_o[_g.id]["_bflag"]=1;
	_o[_g.id]["_bmenu"]=true;
	_o[_g.id]["_limit"]=false;
	_o[_g.id]["_binput"]=false;
	_o[_g.id]["_charlist"]=false;
	_o[_g.id]["_screen"]=false;
	_o[_g.id]["_tips"]=true;
	_o[_g.id]["_cursor"]=true;
	_o[_g.id]["_selectFirst"]=true;
	_o[_g.id]["_css"]="";
	_o[_g.id]["options"]={"_bmenu":{text:"Burglish Menu(F2)"},"_tips":{text:"Tips"},"_cursor":{text:"Follow Cursor"},"_limit":{text:"Known Syllables Only"},"_selectFirst":{text:"Auto-Select First Item"},"_charlist":{text:"Characters List",cb:"sh_chlist"},"_binput":{text:"TypeWriter(F8)"}};
	_o[_g.id]["optgrp"]=["_bmenu_binput"];
	_o[_g.id]["burglish_font"]="Zawgyi_One";
	_o[_g.id]["key"]="WinInnwa";
	for( var item in _g ) { if(item!="id") _o[_g.id][item] = _g[item]; };
	
	if (!skipAttachment) {
	    
	    if($(_g.id)){
		    if($(_g.id).tagName=="TEXTAREA" )	attachTextbox( _g );
	    }else{
		    writeTextbox( _g );
	    }
	    updateChkbox(_g.id);
	}
	
	_dfont=_o[_g.id]["burglish_font"];
};

